sources.title: Human Planet
sources.description: A cinematic experience bringing you the most amazing human stories in the world. Humans and wildlife surviving in the most extreme environments on Earth

metadata.Plot: A groundbreaking documentary that delves deep into an alarming menace: The Douche. This thought-provoking film uncovers the destructive behavior and into the devastating consequences of this on our planet as a whole.
metadata.Actors: Mark Matechuk, Ezio Bondi, Madison Cipparone
